        <li>Attempt to gain unauthorized access to our systems</li>
        <li>Scrape or harvest data from the Site without permission</li>
        <li>Impersonate any person or entity</li>
      </ul>
      
      <h3>4.2 User Content</h3>
      <p>
        If you submit comments or feedback, you grant us a non-exclusive, royalty-free, perpetual license 
        to use, modify, and display that content.
      </p>
    </section>
    
    <section>
      <h2>5. Intellectual Property</h2>
      <p>
        All content on {SITE.name}, including but not limited to text, graphics, logos, images, and software, 
        is the property of {LEGAL.company} or its content suppliers and is protected by United States and 
        international copyright laws.
      </p>
      <p>
        You may view and print content for personal, non-commercial use only. Any other use requires our 
        prior written permission.
      </p>
    </section>
    
    <section>
      <h2>6. Disclaimer of Warranties</h2>
      <p>
        THE SITE AND ALL CONTENT ARE PROVIDED "AS IS" WITHOUT WARRANTIES OF ANY KIND, EXPRESS OR IMPLIED.
      </p>
      <p>
        We do not warrant that:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>The Site will be uninterrupted or error-free</li>
        <li>Defects will be corrected</li>
        <li>The Site is free of viruses or harmful components</li>
        <li>Information provided is accurate, complete, or current</li>
        <li>Products reviewed will meet your expectations</li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        <strong>Product Information:</strong> Prices, availability, and specifications are subject to change. 
        Always verify information with the merchant before making a purchase.
      </p>
    </section>
    
    <section>
      <h2>7. Limitation of Liability</h2>
      <p>
        TO THE FULLEST EXTENT PERMITTED BY LAW, {LEGAL.company} SHALL NOT BE LIABLE FOR ANY:
      </p>
      <ul>
