        Our total liability to you for any claim shall not exceed $100 or the amount you paid us (if any), 
        whichever is less.
      </p>
    </section>
    
    <section>
      <h2>8. Third-Party Links</h2>
      <p>
        Our Site contains links to third-party websites and services. We are not responsible for:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>The content or practices of linked sites</li>
