        <li>Your transactions with merchants</li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        We recommend reading the terms and privacy policies of any third-party sites you visit.
      </p>
    </section>
    
    <section>
      <h2>9. Indemnification</h2>
      <p>
        You agree to indemnify and hold harmless {LEGAL.company}, its affiliates, and their respective 
        officers, directors, and employees from any claims, damages, or expenses arising from:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Your use of the Site</li>
