        Questions about these Terms should be sent to:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:{SITE.email}">{SITE.email}</a></li>
        <li><strong>Website:</strong> <a href="{SITE.url}">{SITE.url}</a></li>
      </ul>
    </section>
    
    <section class="jurisdiction">
      <p><strong>Effective Date:</strong> {LEGAL.lastUpdated}</p>
      <p><strong>Jurisdiction:</strong> {LEGAL.jurisdiction}</p>
      <p><strong>Entity:</strong> {LEGAL.company}</p>
    </section>
